-- Yi Gang Says China Will Do Its Part With `Gradual' Approach on Yuan Value
-- B y   S a n d r i n e   R a s t e l l o
-- 2010-10-07T15:25:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/yi-gang-says-china-will-do-its-part-with-gradual-approach-on-yuan-value.html
The People’s Bank of China’s Vice
Governor Yi Gang said the country will do its part to help
correct imbalances in the world economy.  Speaking in Washington, Yi said China is using a
“gradual” approach on its currency, reiterating that major
changes would cause “social upheaval.”  Yi said a regional currency agreement is unlikely.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sandrine Rastello in Paris at 
 srastello@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
